### System Requirements

{% if language == "python" %}
- **Python 3.10+** required
- Pre-built wheels for Linux (x86_64, aarch64), macOS (arm64, x86_64), Windows (x86_64)
{% elif language == "typescript" %}
- **Node.js 18+** required (NAPI-RS native bindings)
- Pre-built binaries for Linux (x86_64), macOS (arm64, x86_64), Windows (x86_64)
{% elif language == "go" %}
- **Go 1.21+** required; needs `spikard-ffi` static library at link time
{% elif language == "java" %}
- **Java 17+** required
{% elif language == "ruby" %}
- **Ruby 3.2+** required
{% elif language == "php" %}
- **PHP 8.2+** required
{% elif language == "csharp" %}
- **.NET 8.0+** required
{% elif language == "elixir" %}
- **Elixir 1.14+** and **Erlang/OTP 25+** required
{% elif language == "wasm" %}
- Modern browser with WebAssembly support, or Node.js 18+, or Deno 1.0+
{% elif language == "kotlin" %}
- **Kotlin 1.9+ / JVM 17+** required
{% elif language == "dart" %}
- **Dart 3.0+** required
{% elif language == "gleam" %}
- **Gleam 1.0+** and **Erlang/OTP 25+** required
{% elif language == "swift" %}
- **Swift 5.9+** / macOS 13+ or Linux required
{% elif language == "zig" %}
- **Zig 0.13+** required; needs `spikard-ffi` static library at link time
{% elif language == "ffi" %}
- C99 or C++11 compiler; `spikard-ffi` static/shared library from [GitHub Releases](https://github.com/Goldziher/spikard/releases)
{% else %}
- See [Installation Guide](https://github.com/Goldziher/spikard#installation) for requirements
{% endif %}
